		<label>Khyber AK-308 "Cannon"</label>
		<description>Caliber: 7.62x51mm NATO. 10-round detachable mag. Select-Fire.
		
This is a Khyber Pass-produced AK-style rifle that feeds from a makeshift ten-round magazine and fires .308 Winchester/7.62 NATO cartridges. It is quite similar to the Russian Saiga-308 rifle, but this unique specimen was assembled by hand.</description>
